		"Bowl-O-Rama
	]em
	" is a bowling simulator created by P&P Marketing for the arcades.  It uses trackball rolling to throw bowling balls at pins.  It features 3 different game modes: "Bowl-O-Rama" which is just regular bowling, "Flash-O-Matic" which scores you based on timing and performance, and "Blackjack" which gives you cards in blackjack that correspond to the amount of pins you throw in a single frame.
